'''樂高聖經故事'''（The Brick Testament）是由一位名為Brendan Powell Smith的人以[[樂高積木|樂高積木]]及靜態照片[[戲仿|戲仿]]了[[聖經|聖經]]的故事，並把它們都上傳到[[網頁|網頁]]中。該項目從2001年10月由[[創世紀|創世紀]]開始<ref>{{cite news
 | url = http://www.thebricktestament.com/press/philadelphia_inquirer_03_12_11.html
 | author = Rubin, Daniel
 | date = 11 December 2003
 | title = "In the beginning" was a snap.
 | publisher = Philadelphia Inquirer
 | accessdate = 2011-01-29
 | archive-date = 2020-09-09
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200909171142/http://www.thebricktestament.com/press/philadelphia_inquirer_03_12_11.html
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref> ，直到現在還在構造中。除了網頁之外，作者還出版了書籍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/1594740445/thebricktesta-20 |title=The Brick Testament: The Ten Commandments [Hardcover] |access-date=2011-01-29 |archive-date=2005-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050303022842/http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/1594740445/thebricktesta-20/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

被戲仿的內容通常都是以直接地表達，作者也小心地處理了聖經中[[暴力|暴力]]、[[色情|色情]]等的不雅情節。這些插圖往往在引言中加插了一段諷刺性的文字。網頁中一些不雅情節會被標籤為[[裸體|裸體]](N)、色情(S)、暴力(V)及[[詛咒|詛咒]](C)。不過所謂的裸體及暴力內容分別都是用身體部份只是黃色的積木人代表裸體及一些透明紅色的積木塊代表[[血|血]]而已。

據稱作者是一位[[無神論者|無神論者]]，不過作者指出創作網頁的原意是探索聖經經文而不是嘲笑它們。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thebricktestament.com/press/rolling_stone_05_10_06.html |title=6 October 2005 edition of Rolling Stone magazine |access-date=2011-02-01 |archive-date=2020-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909171152/http://www.thebricktestament.com/press/rolling_stone_05_10_06.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

